{"tid":2041481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果真係想港獨 呢樣野好重要快啲入黎傾傾呀喂","createTime":"2020-05-29T09:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T09:39:11.000Z","uid":92376,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6f9c29a0d04f5968dbe3eba4578a37c7283dffcc","tid":2041481,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"就係香港目前既正式英文名Hong Kong<br />\n真係好低級好上唔到國際場面 如果依家既地位係城市 接受都OK 但如果係一個國咁就爭啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全世界既國家啲英文名都係有意思 唔係拼音整出黎咁核突<br />\neven我地最憎既中國 佢地對外都係叫China 而唔係Zhong Guo咁肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但睇返大陸城市例如北京或者武漢就用返拼音 證明國家名同城市名既區分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再望下隔離海既澳門 都唔會就咁叫Auman 而係叫Macau/o 另外台灣都有別名Formosa 至今仍然有好大影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯獨係香港既英文名只係軟弱無力地咁用粵拼既Hong Kong作為國際稱呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因此重新訂立一個香港既官方英文名係有必要性 依家暫時我有兩個方案<br />\n<br />\n1. 直接用香港最有代表性既維多利亞港入面既Victoria 借代香港 簡單易明<br />\n<br />\n2. 將香港意譯做英文 但如果譯過去又會好長 所以我提倡一個混合字<br />\n<br />\na. Fragrant harbour= Fragrbour<br />\n<br />\nb. Prefumed harbour= Prefubour<br />\n<br />\n兩個都可以引申出「芳香的海港」既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結： Hong Kong 呢個名係令到香港呢個地方邊緣化做一個城市既感覺 永遠無左一個被稱為國家既感覺 變相自我矮化 難以達成真正獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475256004d9871bdbe24959f8c195bea4f52dc8a","tid":2041481,"uid":314979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"改個名就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf648918568ef1c50a1e2b571d7c0bf8c4252fc1","tid":2041481,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"475256004d9871bdbe24959f8c195bea4f52dc8a","tid":2041481,"uid":314979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"改個名就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"呢樣野遲做早做都係要做 點解唔依家諗個有共識既好名？"},{"pid":"d517969febbd5a7674d151d1632670faa56c324f","tid":2041481,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:13:43.000Z","msg":"冒住好大勇氣開呢個post 真驚比國安拉<br />\n大家認真討論 thx"},{"pid":"cfdf3b5c2a035f49d0101e5a1162739dd50e567b","tid":2041481,"uid":314979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bf648918568ef1c50a1e2b571d7c0bf8c4252fc1","tid":2041481,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"475256004d9871bdbe24959f8c195bea4f52dc8a","tid":2041481,"uid":314979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"改個名就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"呢樣野遲做早做都係要做 點解唔依家諗個有共識既好名？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:14:04.000Z","msg":"nothing personal<br />\nChing 幾大到"},{"pid":"1bd0eee69ab5596bde1d440c1ae8c52bbecc0549","tid":2041481,"uid":51057,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:14:53.000Z","msg":"名呢D我覺得意義不大, 本身hong kong都已經好地地. 台灣都係就咁叫taiwan啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時真係立到國既, 咪一係叫republic of hong kong囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee8cc281ef97a124f95c71451348408d8d8fb02","tid":2041481,"uid":25099,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"完全冇咁既需要<br />\nHong Kong 兩個字雖然係拼音, 但完全體現到獨特性同歷史"},{"